  "notes": "LOINC choices are aligned to the 2026-07-01 live SD1 bench capture. LDL uses the molar serum/plasma LDL cholesterol term without method-specific calculation because the capture does not prove whether SD1 reports direct or calculated LDL. Crea casing is intentional and must match OBX-3.1 exactly. Bridge code treats MSH-16=1 calibration as a separate non-patient path and MSH-16=2 as QC; OBR-14 carries lot number and OBR-20 carries QC type/level when present."
